'''富士X-Pro3'''是一款[[富士胶片|富士胶片]]的[[無反光鏡可換鏡頭相機|无反光镜可换镜头数码相机]]，发布于2019年10月23日<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=Hands-on with the quirky, retro fantastic Fujifilm X-Pro3|url=https://www.dpreview.com/articles/2118408140/hands-on-with-the-quirky-retro-fantastic-fujifilm-x-pro3|website=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522150551/https://www.dpreview.com/articles/2118408140/hands-on-with-the-quirky-retro-fantastic-fujifilm-x-pro3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=Fujifilm's X-Pro3 can focus in almost complete darkness|url=https://www.engadget.com/2019/10/23/fujifilm-x-pro3-rangefinder-camera/|website=Engadget|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211121043/https://www.engadget.com/2019/10/23/fujifilm-x-pro3-rangefinder-camera/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。此相机是富士X系列相机的一部分，是接替[[富士X-Pro2|富士X-Pro2]]的下一代产品。2019年11月28日开始对外发售<ref>{{cite web|first1=Olivia Tambini 2019-10-23T09:31:54Z|last1=Cameras|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=Fujifilm X-Pro3 delivers retro charm in a high-tech package|url=https://www.techradar.com/uk/news/fujifilm-x-pro3-delivers-retro-charm-in-a-high-tech-package|website=TechRadar|archive-date=2019-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105192620/https://www.techradar.com/uk/news/fujifilm-x-pro3-delivers-retro-charm-in-a-high-tech-package|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

富士X-Pro3是X-Pro系列的最新款。

==特性==
相机的顶部和底部由钛制成，其余的机身外壳则由镁合金制成<ref name="ap">{{cite web|first1=Amateur|last1=Photographer|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=Fujifilm X-Pro3: hands-on first look|url=https://www.amateurphotographer.co.uk/reviews/compactsystemcameras/fujifilm-x-pro3|website=Amateur Photographer|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925214301/http://www.amateurphotographer.co.uk/reviews/compactsystemcameras/fujifilm-x-pro3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 涂覆更耐磨的DuraTect表面涂层的钛顶板和底板的版本于2019年12月8日上市<ref name="theverge">{{cite web|first1=Dan|last1=Seifert|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=Fujifilm’s new X-Pro3 brings analog ideas to a digital camera|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/23/20927225/fujifilm-x-pro3-mirrorless-camera-specs-features-hands-on-demo-test-price-availability|date=23 October 2019|website=The Verge|archive-date=2020-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501154442/https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/23/20927225/fujifilm-x-pro3-mirrorless-camera-specs-features-hands-on-demo-test-price-availability|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=FUJIFILM X-Pro3 {{!}} Cameras|url=https://fujifilm-x.com/zh-cn/products/cameras/x-pro3/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|work=FUJIFILM X Series & GFX -中国|publisher=|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930152651/https://fujifilm-x.com/zh-cn/products/cameras/x-pro3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 有评论指出，之后的表面涂层处理突显了指纹<ref name="ap"/><ref name="theverge"/>。

相比于上一代，这一代提供了双面的翻转屏幕，一面是指示拍摄参数，类似于肩屏的LED显示屏，另一面是预览画面、调整菜单设置的LCD屏幕。不过X-Pro3的翻转屏设计只能让LED小屏幕保持在外面<ref name=":0" />。

X-Pro3没有机内防抖功能，此功能是同时代相机甚至手机的标准配置<ref name="gizmodo">{{cite web|accessdate=2019-10-30|title=The Fujifilm X-Pro3 Is a Love Letter to Street Photography|url=https://gizmodo.com/the-fujifilm-x-pro3-is-a-love-letter-to-street-photogra-1839289036|website=Gizmodo|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810030018/https://gizmodo.com/the-fujifilm-x-pro3-is-a-love-letter-to-street-photogra-1839289036|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 自动对焦可在-6 EV档位工作（接近黑暗）<ref name="gizmodo" />。

X-Pro3采用了新固件算法，富士称旨在充分发挥第四代X-Trans CMOS 4传感器和X-Processor 4的潜力<ref name=":0" />。

富士没有在其中文官网展示X-Pro3的任何信息<ref>{{Cite web|title=数码相机 {{!}} Fujifilm 中国|url=http://www.fujifilm.com.cn/products/digital_cameras/|accessdate=2020-12-14|work=www.fujifilm.com.cn|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610173323/http://www.fujifilm.com.cn/products/digital_cameras/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而是另在专门展示富士X与GFX系列相机的网站展示了X-Pro3。

